# Banana React — Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` for local development and fill in the values.
Never commit `.env.local` or any file containing real secrets.

## Required for all builds

# Base URL for the Banana classification API.
# - Local dev:   http://localhost:3000
# - Vercel preview: https://staging-api.banana.engineer (set in Vercel Preview tier)
# - Production:  https://api.banana.engineer (set in Vercel Production tier)
VITE_BANANA_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

## Optional

# Sentry DSN for browser error tracking.
# Obtain from: https://sentry.io → Projects → banana-react → Client Keys
# Leave empty to disable Sentry (dev/test mode).
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=

# RUM beacon URL for custom Core Web Vitals forwarding (optional).
VITE_RUM_BEACON_URL=
